title: Announcing the winner of the Global AI Film Award
description: Zoubeir Jlassi reacts with surprise on stage at the AI Film Awards for the film "Lily" by Zoubeir Jlassi. He stands by a trophy podium while Anthony Nakache claps. The background shows the film's title and poster.
